cs.CL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel approach to build a language model for software code using deep learning techniques.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a likely category as the paper addresses the issue of capturing long context in software code, which is a common problem in software engineering.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses deep learning-based Long Short Term Memory architecture to build the language model.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes an AI-based approach to model software code.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a possible category as the paper deals with modeling software code, which is a fundamental aspect of programming languages.
